{"tid":1985292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權又幫中聯辦解話","createTime":"2020-04-23T05:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T05:20:57.000Z","uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45c84f5bd3b6ab683f05ef64b13ae48bae53bad1","tid":1985292,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"聶德權稱中聯辦因應立法會內會停擺表達意見屬履行職務<br />\n<br />\n剛退任政制及內地事務局局長的聶德權，早前牽涉基本法22條及中聯辦定位的爭議，他昨日調任為公務員事務局局長。被問到調職是否反映他做錯了甚麼以及是否為了討好北京，聶德權表示，中央駐港機構與特區的關係，政府在不同時期的文件所表述的立場不清晰亦不一致，因此產生問題，當局已在新聞稿交代，行政長官亦有解釋，他再次就修改新聞稿帶來的混亂和誤解致歉。聶德權又指，目前的核心焦點是中聯辦因應立法會內會停擺導致香港的整體情況，表達意見及評論，屬於履行職務。<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-23 12:54:29"},{"pid":"4e970a5bb539c69d92525a13ec4e86723398493e","tid":1985292,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYVNsYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYVNsYc.png&h=cc7811e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fc14dc30b7a01df119b6ff788d48c4a8e144150","tid":1985292,"uid":205162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"被人收左皮都咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5851b35692e717c986f384dc0b55ed6b548eef","tid":1985292,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4608d9dcaadd3668b77c52da2d472018257d1146","tid":1985292,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"繼續追擊22條，尤其國際戰要打擊鬼佬投資者對香港信心，比佢地知道憲政秩序受動搖，在港投資分分鍾渣都無"},{"pid":"fc577879f23f14ea78e57fdcb8aa387e0d577ac5","tid":1985292,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gi